{"tid":1547752,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"《返校》出咗 iOS  幾好玩","createTime":"2019-09-06T18:48:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T12:22:28.000Z","uid":152559,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e13e7787fc06ed8d0a5dbc33c564a7df598d54b7","tid":1547752,"uid":152559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:48:26.000Z","msg":"最鍾意玩恐怖 game    <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8751fc4602f0a44b434c48e86806f63604664660","tid":1547752,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:48:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一句講晒，睇哩個post</span></span><br />\n[置頂/請廣傳/多圖] 907 遊客LOOK 暢遊大嶼山指南<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547426</a>"},{"pid":"18c1fc5ba65ee967074f05afed024814c898352d","tid":1547752,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:48:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1571498d28001b3e49a023ef0c036685928806e7","tid":1547752,"uid":57221,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:49:15.000Z","msg":"已經有人企出黎話朋友係831太子俾popo打死，快推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547651\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547651</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cc8e1ffb8a8bfa530bcae756c99bd65daa4c2690","tid":1547752,"uid":145664,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:49:54.000Z","msg":"907 機場攻略(濃縮版)<br />\n無時無刻緊記自己普通市民/旅客身份<br />\n<br />\n- 一定要提早到機場！ 最好十二點已經係機場<br />\n- 市民/旅客裝，唔着黑色衫，唔叫口號，可以戴普通口罩，唔需要其他裝備<br />\n- 地點: 暢達路巴士總站 或者 暢航路<br />\n- 交通: 優先搭巴士入，建議大家首先 集合左係青馬收費廣場 再搭巴士入機場，機場快線去 香港站<br />\n- 青馬收費廣場係交通樽頸，如果所有途徑巴士都要埋站會好影響交通；同樣，香港站一停，機鐵就送唔到遊客去機場<br />\n- 如果巴士唔停青馬收費廣場就直接入機場；如果直接停A同E機場巴士服務，旅客要搭巴士入機場就唯有 去東涌<br />\n- 策略: 到左機場唔一定要企定等， 緊記市民/旅客身份 ，可以係周圍行行企企，排下隊，落車上車<br />\n<br />\n- 無論如何都唔好係 T1/2 機場客運大樓附近設路障塞路 ，即使有任何行動都一定要 等到三點 後全部人入左機場先<br />\n<br />\n關於清場/逃走路線<br />\n- 無時無刻緊記自己普通市民/旅客身份 ，萬一警察真係清場，記得 緊貼其他遊客 ，佢地去邊大家就去邊， 普通市民/旅客冇犯法係唔需要逃走 <br />\n- 有咩合理原因可以係機場範圍出現？接機/送機，參觀機場，巴士/地鐵愛好者，即興旅行，等等<br />\n<br />\n- 密切留意睇Telegram頻道: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2vMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=58883fc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n機場Fact Check Channel: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/fcairport\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffcairport&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2vMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=deff935f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/fcairport</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WjFkzL9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWjFkzL9.png&h=b1adcf9b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0SGvWZu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0SGvWZu.png&h=3dddac2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ja1jcQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ja1jcQ.png&h=4ae2cb47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UpztJEv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUpztJEv.jpg&h=bbc66c7e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xsPQWZv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxsPQWZv.jpg&h=d8769fc7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eUH7eMb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeUH7eMb.jpg&h=f486c2cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4274e4315c1dbcf2696a9c9a5b49110bf551c23","tid":1547752,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T21:16:22.000Z","msg":"政治game嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f67b27971f383089ba1765f5055215046919f4f","tid":1547752,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T23:54:37.000Z","